@startuml variant_a_seq_failover
title Вариант A - failover сценарий (push упал, SMS доставлено)

participant "Kafka" as K
participant "Delivery\nEngine" as DE
participant "Delivery DB" as DDB
participant "Push\nAdapter" as PA
participant "FCM" as FCM
participant "SMS\nAdapter" as SA
participant "SMS\nПровайдер" as SMS
participant "Пользователь" as U

K --> DE : Consume(txn.notifications)
DE -> DDB : INSERT delivery(status = PENDING)

DE -> PA : Send push(device_token, payload)
PA -> FCM : POST /fcm/send
FCM --> PA : 503 Service Unavailable

note over PA : circuit breaker\nпереходит в OPEN

PA --> DE : error
DE -> DDB : UPDATE status = PUSH_FAILED

DE -> DDB : UPDATE status = FAILOVER_SMS

DE -> SA : Send SMS(phone, text)
SA -> SMS : POST /sms/send (провайдер 1)
SMS --> SA : 200 OK (sms_id)
SA --> DE : accepted

note over DE : Ожидание receipt\n(таймаут 25 сек)

SMS -> U : SMS
SMS -> DE : POST /webhook\n{ status: delivered, sms_id }
DE -> DDB : UPDATE status = DELIVERED

note over U : P99 <= 30 сек от события

@enduml
